    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $31,900, this vehicle is in good overall condition and should make a solid choice for someone looking for a clean, well-kept driver. It runs and drives well, presents nicely inside and out, and shows the kind of normal age-related wear you would expect from a car that has been used and maintained rather than stored away as a showpiece. Overall, it\u2019s an honest, appealing example that should suit someone who wants a dependable vehicle they can enjoy right away.",
