    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$47,900 - Exceptional mint-condition example that shows beautifully and has clearly been very well cared for. The exterior presents extremely clean with excellent paint, strong trim and glass, and the kind of overall finish that stands out right away. Inside, the cabin is equally impressive, with a very fresh, well-preserved appearance and minimal signs of age or wear. This is the kind of car a buyer can feel good about showing, collecting, or simply enjoying as a top-tier driver, with the expectation of a clean, highly sorted, standout example rather than a project or rough-around-the-edges car.",
      "price": 47900.0,
