    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle is a practical low-cost option for buyers who want dependable basic transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with a well-used car, but it still offers real value at an accessible price point. If you're looking for an inexpensive way to get on the road without overpaying, this is a smart buy.",
