      "description": "Honest little project car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect and it shows, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone handy, in need of cheap wheels, or looking for a solid fixer-upper to make their own. Priced fairly and represented honestly by a seller who believes in straightforward deals.",
